{
  "id": "adv_main_02_02_02",
  "title": "東京編1章7話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_impact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE is going to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "星見プロに移籍！！？？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…sign with Hoshimi Productions?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6666666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "正式に決まった訳じゃない。そう申し出があったんだ\n意見も聞きたかったから、その場では決断出来なかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not official yet‚ but they did ask to be signed.\nI wanted to hear your thoughts‚ so I couldn’t give them an answer then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ずいぶん急な話ですわね\n理由は分かりませんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is all quite sudden.\nDon’t you know their reasons?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.066666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "事務所をクビにされちゃうって、よっぽどの\nことをしちゃった……ってこと？　でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they got fired from their agency‚ wouldn’t that mean\nthey did something… really bad? But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。鈴村さん達は、そういう問題を起こすような\n人達じゃないよ。話したことがあるから、分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Rui-san‚ Yu-san‚ and Sumire-san aren’t the type of people\nwho would cause trouble. I know based on our conversations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.82204058965048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、移籍はありなんじゃないかな？\n星見プロに来てくれたら、きっと楽しいだろうし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ why don’t we sign them?\nIf they joined Hoshimi Productions‚ we’d all have a lot of fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.85705184936525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "確かにー！　きっと賑やかになるよね\n芽衣も、会っていろいろお喋りしたいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knowww! Things would get pretty lively here.\nI’d love to meet them and talk to them‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.302586432865695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 46.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。みんな、怪しいと思わないの？\n理由もなくクビって、不当解雇ってことでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not so fast. Guys‚ don’t you think this is a little suspicious?\nIf he fired them without reason‚ that’s a wrongful termination.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.23591976619903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "立派な、労基法、違反……でも、\nバンプロみたいな大手が、そんなこと……する？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A perfect violation… of the Labor Standards Act. But…\nWould a major company like Van Productions do a thing like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.46113518533254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか……解雇されたと偽って星見プロに潜入して\n内部事情を探る企業スパイに……なんて、まさかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t think… they lied about being fired so they could infiltrate Hoshimi Productions\nand become spies‚ sniffing out confidential info? It couldn’t be that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.39446851866586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにそこまでしないと思いますけど……\nただ、怪しいと感じるのは同意見ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I highly doubt it’s anything that extreme.\nBut I do agree. This is suspicious behavior.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.16113518533254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルほどの実力と人気なら\n大手の事務所からも引く手数多のはずだろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A group as talented and popular as TRINITYAiLE\nwould have lots of big agencies trying to snatch them up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.52780185199921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……いやいや、うちだって十分頑張ってて\n結構大きくなったんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good point… No‚ wait‚ our agency isn’t doing bad either.\nWe’ve gotten pretty big‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.26113518533256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ものの例えですって。それぐらいトリエルの\n持ち出した話が怪しいってことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was an example. I’m just illustrating\nwhy TRINITYAiLE’s story doesn’t add up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.32780185199924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "難しく考えなくていいと思うけどな～\nだって、本当に困ってるのかもしれないよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think we need to overanalyze it‚ really.\nI mean‚ they might really need our help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.62780185199924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "安易に信用しない方がいいわよ\n曲がりなりにも、ライバル事務所のアイドルなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn’t trust them so quickly.\nThey’re idols from our rival agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.96113518533257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、その事務所をクビになったんですわよね？\nでしたら、関係ないんじゃありませんこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that agency fired them‚ no?\nSo‚ wouldn’t that no longer apply?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6944685186659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、落ち着いて。どうしてうちを選んだのかって\n理由は、本人達に聞けばいい。けど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now‚ calm down. If we want to know why they came to us‚\nwe could just ask them directly. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.12780185199928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それよりも先に、話を聞かないといけない人がいる\nこれからちょっと会いに行ってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before we do that‚ there’s someone else I need to talk…\nI’ll go visit him from now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.80061386880445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "話を聞く人……誰なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone else you want to talk? Who?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.96728053547113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 139.70061386880454
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 139.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 143.26728053547114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ここがバンプロのビルなんだ～\nなんだか、ちょっとワクワクするね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is Van Productions!\nI’m feeling kinda excited!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.26728053547117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 146.23394720213784
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "はしゃがないの。これから大事な話をしに行くんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down. We’re about to have an important talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.23394720213784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 150.60383383887185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。話すのは主に俺なんだけど……\nていうか、何でついてきてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Though I’m going to be the one doing most of the talking.\nIn fact‚ why are you two here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.50383383887169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 156.83716717220543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "だって、星見プロにとっても、一大事なんですよ？\n一人で背負う必要はありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on! This is very important for Hoshimi Productions‚ isn’t it?\nYou needn’t carry the burden all alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8705005055384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 163.5705005055384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "昨日も、話したじゃないですか\nもう少し信用して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We discussed this yesterday‚ remember?\nYou need to trust us a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9038338388718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 168.23420397894748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だからってここまで首突っ込まなくても……\nまあでも……心配してくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but you don’t need to get this involved…\nWell‚ then again… thanks for caring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.6008706456143,
