      "text": "ええ、朝倉さんこそお元気そうで何よりです\n急なお約束なのにありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. It’s good to see you’re in good health‚ Asakura-san.\nThank you for agreeing to meet with me on such short notice.",
