      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういえば、聞いたよ。三枝のやつが失踪したとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I heard the news. Saegusa vanished‚ eh?",
        "id": ""
